<br>
On Hard advs when I lull pull the difference between instacast pulling and 3 second HoS pulling can be the difference between a single pull and adds.  A lot of times I land a lull on the first target then get multiple resists on the next target.  30 seconds on lull goes fast when you keep getting resists. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub147.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=trobb>Trobb</A></span><br> Posts: 4<br> <font color=#330000>(3/25/04 3:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19197.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: if you pull...</span><hr size=1> Our pacify song doesn't always last for the max amount.  Multiply this for pacifying multiple mobs. Now combine this with the abilty to target the mob you want to pull as you are casting pacify on a different mob.  The result is awesome.<br>
